data.description: One-story living with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths located in Heritage Farms subdivision. This great home offers a fresh sleek look with solid countertops,  plenty of cabinet space, a kitchen island, walk in pantry that serves as the laundry room as well. Tile floor throughout, the garage was converted. Great sized rooms, along with a spacious backyard boasting a shed and a concrete slab covered patio. Mature trees and privacy fencing. Conveniently located next to countless restaurants, and shopping.
